UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 1909
1 Webb; and her great-grandson, Eli Messer;
2 NOW, THEREFORE,
3 Be it resolved by the House of Representatives of the General Assembly of the
4 Commonwealth of Kentucky:
5 Section 1. The members of the House of Representatives do hereby honor the
6 life and accomplishments of former Governor Martha Layne Collins and posthumously
7 recognize her for the demonstrated dedication and service to the Commonwealth of
8 Kentucky and its citizens.
9 Section 2. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
10 Resolution to Representative Lindsey Burke for delivery to Dr. Bill Collins.
